Model.Name: Tutorial_10
Model.Description: This tutorial explains how to use daeModel functions d() and dt() that calculate time- and partial-derivative of an expression (not of a single variable), how to use initialization files (.init) and how to use mathematical operators which operate on both adouble and adouble_array.
